OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773943560
OL,3,CRare monkey gives birth after
OL,4,Cpioneering operation to save foot
OL,6,FAn endangered monkey, whose foot was
OL,7,Fsaved from amputation thanks to
OL,8,Fpioneering surgery, has given birth.
OL,10,FFifteen-year-old roloway monkey Masaya
OL,11,Fwelcomed infant Lagertha months after
OL,12,Fa complex operation to remove a golf
OL,13,Fball-sized mass from her foot.
OL,15,FDespite finding no previous examples
OL,16,Fof the surgery on roloway monkeys,
OL,17,Fvets at Chester Zoo teamed up with
OL,18,Fsurgeons from the University of
OL,19,FLiverpool and adapted surgical
OL,20,Ftechniques for the procedure last
OL,21,Fsummer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773943560
OL,3,CRare monkey gives birth after
OL,4,Cpioneering operation to save foot
OL,6,FThe operation meant they were able to
OL,7,Fsave all but one of Masaya's toes.
OL,9,FZoe Edwards, primate keeper at Chester
OL,10,FZoo, said: "Masaya is a very
OL,11,Fexperienced mum and she's parenting
OL,12,Fmagnificently.
OL,14,F"Lagertha is only a few weeks old and
OL,15,Fis very dinky but already curious
OL,16,Fabout the roloway monkey habitat and
OL,17,Finquisitive about us.
OL,26,@rD@LOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773943560
OL,3,CRare monkey gives birth after
OL,4,Cpioneering operation to save foot
OL,6,F"The fact Masaya's foot has healed so
OL,7,Fwell is a huge relief. If she'd had an
OL,8,Famputation, we'd have been left with
OL,9,Freal questions about whether she could
OL,10,Fhold her offspring or continue with
OL,11,Fher normal behaviours."
OL,13,FLagertha, named after a Viking queen,
OL,14,Fis just over four weeks old and about
OL,15,Fthe size of a tennis ball.
OL,17,FThe zoo is one of two places in the UK
OL,18,Fwhere roloway monkeys can be found and
OL,19,Fthere are only a few breeding females
OL,20,Fin Europe, Ms Edwards said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
