FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773943560
OL,3,CRare monkey gives birth after
OL,4,Cpioneering operation to save foot
OL,6,FFewer than 2,000 of the monkeys live
OL,7,Fin the wild in Ghana and the Ivory
OL,8,FCoast, where they face habitat loss
OL,9,Fand poaching, according to the
OL,10,FInternational Union for Conservation
OL,11,Fof Nature.
OL,13,FMasaya, now a mother-of-three, had
OL,14,Fbeen suffering recurring problems with
OL,15,Fher foot since she arrived in Chester
OL,16,Fin 2023 and vets believe the abscess
OL,17,Fmay have been caused by an old thorn
OL,18,Finjury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773943560
OL,3,CRare monkey gives birth after
OL,4,Cpioneering operation to save foot
OL,6,FWhen swelling worsened last year she
OL,7,Fwas taken to the University of
OL,8,FLiverpool Small Animal Teaching
OL,9,FHospital for a CT scan.
OL,11,FCharlotte Bentley, veterinary officer
OL,12,Fat the zoo's animal health centre,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Following the scan, we decided
OL,14,Fan operation was the way forward.
OL,16,F"She's been an absolute trooper all
OL,17,Fthe way through and I'm just glad we
OL,18,Fwere able to do something for her."
OL,26,@uD@GOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
