PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773943560
OL,3,CRare monkey gives birth after
OL,4,Cpioneering operation to save foot
OL,6,FRachel Burrow, vet and lecturer at the
OL,7,FUniversity of Liverpool, added:
OL,8,F"Working with primates is completely
OL,9,Fdifferent from my usual patients, who
OL,10,Fare typically cats and dogs, and it
OL,11,Fwas a real privilege to care for such
OL,12,Fa rare animal.
OL,14,F"It's great to see the surgery was a
OL,15,Fsuccess ` she's comfortable, active
OL,16,Fand using the limb well."
OL,18,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
